<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-fontmetrics.xml">FontMetrics</db:link> calculates the size of characters and strings for a given font.</db:para>
<db:para>It provides a subset of the C++ <db:link xlink:href="qfontmetricsf.xml">QFontMetricsF</db:link> API, with the added ability to change the font that is used for calculations via the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-fontmetrics.xml#font-prop">font</db:link> property.</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">FontMetrics {
    id: fontMetrics
    font.family: &quot;Arial&quot;
}

Rectangle {
    width: fontMetrics.height * 4
    height: fontMetrics.height * 2
}
</db:programlisting>
