<db:section xml:id="advanceWidth-method">
<db:title>qreal advanceWidth(string <db:emphasis>text</db:emphasis>)</db:title>
<db:para>This method returns the advance in pixels of the characters in <db:code role="parameter">text</db:code>. This is the distance from the position of the string to where the next string should be drawn.</db:para>
<db:para>This method is offered as an imperative alternative to the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-textmetrics.xml#advanceWidth-prop">advanceWidth</db:link> property of <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-textmetrics.xml">TextMetrics</db:link>.</db:para>
