<db:section xml:id="boundingRect-method">
<db:title>rect boundingRect(string <db:emphasis>text</db:emphasis>)</db:title>
<db:para>This method returns the bounding rectangle of the characters in the string specified by <db:code role="parameter">text</db:code>.</db:para>
<db:para>This method is offered as an imperative alternative to the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-textmetrics.xml#boundingRect-prop">boundingRect</db:link> property of <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-textmetrics.xml">TextMetrics</db:link>.</db:para>
